title: Comedian Friday (DC Young Fly Interview and Flame Monroe Interview)
itunes:title: Comedian Friday (DC Young Fly Interview and Flame Monroe Interview)
description:
Today on the show we had comedian and now R&B artist DC Young Fly stop by, where he spoke about transitioning into R&B, Wild n Out, and more. Also, we had friend to the room and enemy to some of our listeners Flame Monroe stop by where she spoke about Wendy Williams, presidential election and more. Also Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to yet another Florida man this time because he left a trail of pill bottles for the police to find them after a robbery.
